item.title: Run.bat error
item.dc:creator: @swiftclanhype swiftclanhype
item.description:
@swiftclanhype wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:2, topic:546138”]You’re trying to run a file compiled on a JDK version that is higher than your JRE version.
Upgrade your JRE to Java 1.8 or recompile on JDK 1.7[/quote]
thanks man this really helped me
